00:00:01.494 --> 00:00:07.470 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:07.470 --> 00:00:25.398 align:middle line:90%


00:00:25.398 --> 00:00:28.884 align:middle line:90%
[TRAIN CHUGS]

00:00:28.884 --> 00:00:41.832 align:middle line:90%


00:00:41.832 --> 00:00:46.812 align:middle line:90%
[BIRD SCREECHES]

00:00:46.812 --> 00:00:52.290 align:middle line:90%


00:00:52.290 --> 00:00:56.274 align:middle line:90%
