00:00:56.274 --> 00:01:03.465 align:middle line:90%


00:01:03.465 --> 00:01:06.447 align:middle line:90%
[FILM PROJECTOR CLICKS]

00:01:06.447 --> 00:01:10.920 align:middle line:90%
