All along the edge of Lake
Nicaragua near Granada

00:39:45.890 --> 00:39:50.230 align:middle line:90%
are all of these basalt islands.

00:39:50.230 --> 00:39:51.900 align:middle line:84%
Today, people are
building houses

00:39:51.900 --> 00:39:53.780 align:middle line:90%
on some of these islands.

00:39:53.780 --> 00:39:57.410 align:middle line:84%
They appear to be
artificial, in fact.

00:39:57.410 --> 00:39:59.480 align:middle line:84%
Although it's been
thought for many years

00:39:59.480 --> 00:40:01.830 align:middle line:90%
that they're natural islands.

00:40:01.830 --> 00:40:06.610 align:middle line:84%
