like this known as Nan Madol.

00:40:11.460 --> 00:40:16.260 align:middle line:84%
And it has over 100 artificial
islands just like this

00:40:16.260 --> 00:40:18.320 align:middle line:90%
made out of basalt.

00:40:18.320 --> 00:40:22.806 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:40:22.806 --> 00:40:43.340 align:middle line:90%


