discovered something

00:40:50.437 --> 00:40:51.770 align:middle line:90%
that we think is very important.

00:40:51.770 --> 00:40:54.930 align:middle line:84%
It looks like some of these
islands are in fact artificial

00:40:54.930 --> 00:40:56.900 align:middle line:90%
and have pyramids on them.

