and investigate what appears

00:41:03.830 --> 00:41:05.760 align:middle line:90%
to be a giant basalt pyramid.

00:41:05.760 --> 00:41:12.980 align:middle line:90%


00:41:12.980 --> 00:41:15.670 align:middle line:84%
Landing on the artificial
island with the pyramid

00:41:15.670 --> 00:41:17.880 align:middle line:84%
