discovered, everything

00:41:17.880 --> 00:41:20.420 align:middle line:84%
about this unusual
place seems to be

00:41:20.420 --> 00:41:22.380 align:middle line:84%
that this is some
ancient pyramid

00:41:22.380 --> 00:41:27.550 align:middle line:84%
on this island, giant
blocks of basalt stacked up.

00:41:27.550 --> 00:41:35.270 align:middle line:90%


00:41:35.270 --> 00:41:39.800 align:middle line:84%
What we see here on this
island is rocks piled up.

00:41:39.800 --> 00:41:45.255 align:middle line:84%
You see certain levels of
terracing, very large basalt

00:41:45.255 --> 00:41:46.055 align:middle line:90%
blocks.

00:41:46.055 --> 00:41:49.030 align:middle line:90%


00:41:49.030 --> 00:41:51.730 align:middle line:84%
It seems incredible to me that
they're just here naturally.

00:41:51.730 --> 00:41:53.530 align:middle line:84%
They appear to
have been piled up.

00:41:53.530 --> 00:41:55.846 align:middle line:90%
But it's difficult to tell.

00:41:55.846 --> 00:42:00.328 align:middle line:90%
